---
// SixSystems.astro — Dark indigo section with 6 capability cards
---

<section class="six-wrap">
  <div class="six-bg-fx"></div>

  <div class="six-head">
    <div class="six-badge">
      <span class="mint-dot"></span>
      <span>CORE CAPABILITIES</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="six-title">
      Six AI systems.<br/>
      <span class="grad-mint">One command center.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="six-sub">
      Every feature is connected. Every insight is actionable. Every action is explainable.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="six-grid">
    <article class="ai-card lavender">
      <div class="card-tag"><span>AI · BRAIN</span></div>
      <h3>AI Growth Brain</h3>
      <p>A multi-agent system with 12 specialized AI agents. Your virtual Head of Growth, available 24/7.</p>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="chip">Multi-agent</span>
        <span class="chip">Always-on</span>
        <span class="chip">Autonomous</span>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ai-card mint">
      <div class="card-tag"><span>REV · SHIELD</span></div>
      <h3>Revenue Shield</h3>
      <p>Real-time monitoring of MRR, LTV, ROAS, and subscription health. Detects revenue threats instantly.</p>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="chip">MRR tracking</span>
        <span class="chip">ROAS monitor</span>
        <span class="chip">LTV curves</span>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ai-card cyan">
      <div class="card-tag"><span>FOR · ENGINE</span></div>
      <h3>Forecast Engine</h3>
      <p>Predicts your app's financial status 12 to 90 days ahead. Know when ROAS will drop before it does.</p>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="chip">90-day forecast</span>
        <span class="chip">Scenarios</span>
        <span class="chip">Confidence bands</span>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ai-card pink">
      <div class="card-tag"><span>ACT · AUTONOMOUS</span></div>
      <h3>Autonomous Actions</h3>
      <p>AI suggests. You approve. AI executes. Budget changes, adset pauses, A/B tests — one click.</p>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="chip">One-click execute</span>
        <span class="chip">Audit trail</span>
        <span class="chip">Reversible</span>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ai-card amber">
      <div class="card-tag"><span>BEN · INTEL</span></div>
      <h3>Benchmark Intelligence</h3>
      <p>Compare your CPI, D7 retention, ROAS against 2,400+ apps in your category. Know where you stand.</p>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="chip">Industry benchmarks</span>
        <span class="chip">Percentile</span>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="ai-card coral">
      <div class="card-tag"><span>ALT · WARNING</span></div>
      <h3>Early Warning System</h3>
      <p>Detects creative fatigue, audience saturation, and churn spikes 72 hours before standard dashboards.</p>
      <div class="tag-row">
        <span class="chip">72h early</span>
        <span class="chip">Slack alerts</span>
        <span class="chip">Root cause AI</span>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .six-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0A0070 0%, #11008F 60%, #1A0FB5 100%);
    padding: 80px 24px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .six-bg-fx {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.10) 0%, transparent 50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .six-head {
    position: relative;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .six-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.3);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #10F0A0;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .mint-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #10F0A0;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px #10F0A0;
  }

  .six-title {
    color: white;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .grad-mint {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10F0A0, #5CFFC8);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 24px rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.4));
  }

  .six-sub {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .six-grid {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.10);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .ai-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
  }

  .ai-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
  }

  .ai-card.lavender::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #C4B5FD, transparent); }
  .ai-card.mint::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #10F0A0, transparent); }
  .ai-card.cyan::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #22D3EE, transparent); }
  .ai-card.pink::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #F472B6, transparent); }
  .ai-card.amber::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #FBBF24, transparent); }
  .ai-card.coral::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #FF7A7A, transparent); }

  .card-tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .card-tag span {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
  }

  .ai-card.lavender .card-tag { background: rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.3); }
  .ai-card.lavender .card-tag span { color: #C4B5FD; }

  .ai-card.mint .card-tag { background: rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.3); }
  .ai-card.mint .card-tag span { color: #10F0A0; }

  .ai-card.cyan .card-tag { background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.3); }
  .ai-card.cyan .card-tag span { color: #22D3EE; }

  .ai-card.pink .card-tag { background: rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.3); }
  .ai-card.pink .card-tag span { color: #F472B6; }

  .ai-card.amber .card-tag { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3); }
  .ai-card.amber .card-tag span { color: #FBBF24; }

  .ai-card.coral .card-tag { background: rgba(255, 122, 122, 0.18); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 122, 122, 0.3); }
  .ai-card.coral .card-tag span { color: #FF7A7A; }

  .ai-card h3 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .ai-card p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  .tag-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .chip {
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
  }

  .ai-card.lavender .chip { background: rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.25); color: #DDD6FE; }
  .ai-card.mint .chip { background: rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(16, 240, 160, 0.25); color: #6EE7B7; }
  .ai-card.cyan .chip { background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.25); color: #67E8F9; }
  .ai-card.pink .chip { background: rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(244, 114, 182, 0.25); color: #F9A8D4; }
  .ai-card.amber .chip { background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.25); color: #FCD34D; }
  .ai-card.coral .chip { background: rgba(255, 122, 122, 0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 122, 122, 0.25); color: #FCA5A5; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .six-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .six-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
